/**
* Test if a double-precision floating-point numeric value is `NaN`.
*
* @module @stdlib/math-base-assert-is-nan
*
* @example
* var isnan = require( '@stdlib/math-base-assert-is-nan' );
*
* var bool = isnan( NaN );
* // returns true
*
* bool = isnan( 7.0 );
* // returns false
*/
// MODULES //

var isnan = require('./main.js'); // EXPORTS //
